properties.Description: The properties of an IoT Central application.

sku.Description: Information about the SKU of the IoT Central application.

identity.Description: Managed service identity (either system assigned, or none)

location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

provisioningState.Description: The provisioning state of the application.

displayName.Description: The display name of the application.

template.Description: The ID of the application template, which is a blueprint that defines the characteristics and behaviors of an application. Optional; if not specified, defaults to a blank blueprint and allows the application to be defined from scratch.

state.Description: The current state of the application.

publicNetworkAccess.Description: Whether requests from the public network are allowed.

networkRuleSets.Description: Network Rule Set Properties of this IoT Central application.

privateEndpointConnections.Description: Private endpoint connections created on this IoT Central application.

applyToDevices.Description: Whether these rules apply for device connectivity to IoT Hub and Device Provisioning service associated with this application.

applyToIoTCentral.Description: Whether these rules apply for connectivity via IoT Central web portal and APIs.

defaultAction.Description: Whether to allow or deny network traffic.

filterName.Description: The readable name of the IP rule.

ipMask.Description: The CIDR block defining the IP range.

properties.Description: Properties of the private endpoint connection.

id.Description: Fully qualified resource ID for the resource. Ex - /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/{resourceProviderNamespace}/{resourceType}/{resourceName}

type.Description: The type of the resource. E.g. "Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines" or "Microsoft.Storage/storageAccounts"

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

groupIds.Description: The group ids for the private endpoint resource.

privateLinkServiceConnectionState.Description: A collection of information about the state of the connection between service consumer and provider.

id.Description: The ARM identifier for private endpoint.

description.Description: The reason for approval/rejection of the connection.

actionsRequired.Description: A message indicating if changes on the service provider require any updates on the consumer.

createdBy.Description: The identity that created the resource.

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource.

lastModifiedBy.Description: The identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource.

lastModifiedAt.Description: The timestamp of resource last modification (UTC)

principalId.Description: The service principal ID of the system assigned identity. This property will only be provided for a system assigned identity.

tenantId.Description: The tenant ID of the system assigned identity. This property will only be provided for a system assigned identity.

type.Description: Type of managed service identity (either system assigned, or none).

properties.Description: Properties of the private endpoint connection.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.
